  <summary date="2019-09-26T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Greg LeMond Congressional Gold Medal Act

This bill directs the Speaker of the House of Representatives and the President pro tempore of the Senate to arrange for the presentation of a Congressional Gold Medal to Greg LeMond, in recognition of his contributions to the&#160;United States&#160;as an athlete, activist, role model, and community leader.</summary>
